divs: Sighting DetailsWas checking out the north east sky because of hearing about a visible comet when something cought my attention out of the corner of my eye out of the north north eastern sky . I changed my position to see what it was . about ten seconds later I saw in a dark are of the sky a light slowly apear and become bright then two to three seconds later dim to nothing . at first I thought maybe an aircrafts blinking lights . then again about ten seconds later it again repeated what I had seen . it did this three or four times in what apeared to be the same place in the sky . I contineud to watch but did not see tthe light any more . I was suprised that for as bright as the light would become I could not see any other typeof light that would normaly be seen with a airplane or helicopter
